==未來計畫==

灣區捷運局目前有数個延伸提议：

# 費利蒙南延線：由[[費利蒙站|費利蒙站]]向南經[[诺曼·峰田圣何塞国际机场|聖荷西國際機場]]至聖塔克拉拉的加州通勤火車。費利蒙站至溫泉／南費利蒙站（Warm Springs/South Fremont）已於2017年完工並通車，後續可能在其中增加爾文頓站（Irvington）<ref name="BARTWarmSprings">{{cite web | language = en | publisher = BART | title = Warm Springs Extension Project Overview | url = http://www.bart.gov/about/projects/wsx | date = 2014-03-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151008164355/http://www.bart.gov/about/projects/wsx | archivedate = 2015-10-08 }}</ref>。溫泉／南費利蒙站往南延伸至米爾皮塔斯和聖何塞貝里埃薩地區已于2020年6月13日通车。
# 都柏林／普萊森頓東延線：由[[都柏林／普萊森頓站|都柏林／普萊森頓站]]向東延伸至[[利佛摩_(加利福尼亞州)|利佛摩]]<ref name="BARTtoLivermore">{{cite web | language = en | publisher = BART | title = BART seeks public comment on extension to Livermore | url = http://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2009/news20091103.aspx | date = 2009-11-03 | access-date = 2009-11-11 | archive-date = 2020-11-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201125130942/http://www.bart.gov/news/articles/2009/news20091103.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

